starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.model

Class _Statistics.AnnualData

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.model._Statistics.AnnualData
  • Enclosing class:
    _Statistics

    public class _Statistics.AnnualData
extends java.lang.Object
    Nested class that stores regional information for a particular year. This is held by the RegionalData class so that it can organize all the information for the region according to year.
